@startuml DangerMonitor_SP_Association_GetByUserNameList_Detailed
!theme plain
title CTS_DC_Association_GetByUserNameList - Detailed Database Flow

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor lightblue
    BorderColor darkblue
}

skinparam database {
    BackgroundColor lightyellow
    BorderColor orange
}

skinparam arrow {
    Color darkgreen
}

package "MySQL Database: CTS_DataCenter" {
    database "CTSCustomer" as CTSCustomer
    database "AssociationByDevice" as AssocByDevice
    database "AssociationByAI" as AssocByAI
    database "AssociationGroupByAI" as AssocGroupByAI
    database "AssociationByIP" as AssocByIP
    database "AssociationTypeSetting" as AssocTypeSetting
}

component "CTS_DC_Association_GetByUserNameList" as SP {
    note right
        **Database:** CTS_DataCenter (MySQL)
        **Purpose:** Get Associated Accounts by Username List
        **Association Types:**
        - Device (Type 1)
        - Betting Pattern/AI (Type 2)
        - IP (Type 4)
        **Parameters:**
        - ip_UserNameList: Comma-separated usernames
        - ip_HasDevice: Include Device associations
        - ip_HasAI: Include Betting Pattern associations
        - ip_HasIP: Include IP associations
    end note
}

' Temp Tables
package "Temp Tables (Internal)" {
    component "Temp_Username" as TmpUsername
    component "Temp_Cust" as TmpCust
    component "Temp_Association" as TmpAssociation
    component "Temp_CustDevice" as TmpCustDevice
    component "Temp_AssociationByAI_AssType" as TmpAIAssType
    component "Temp_CustGroupByAI" as TmpCustGroupByAI
    component "Temp_AssociationByIP_AssType" as TmpIPAssType
}

note right of TmpCust
    **Temp Table: Temp_Cust**
    * CTSCustID : BIGINT UNSIGNED
    * CustID : BIGINT UNSIGNED
    **Purpose:** Map Username to CTSCustID and CustID
end note

note right of TmpAssociation
    **Temp Table: Temp_Association**
    * RootCustID : BIGINT UNSIGNED
    * AssCustID : BIGINT UNSIGNED
    * AssociationType : INT
    **Purpose:** Store all found associations
    **Types:** 1=Device, 2=BettingPattern, 4=IP
end note

' Flow: Parse Input Parameters
SP --> TmpUsername : **INSERT**\n(Parse @ip_UserNameList)
note right of SP
    **Parse Logic:**
    - Split comma-separated usernames
    - Use dynamic SQL to insert
    - Example: '12BETGBP01001,307HK'
end note

SP --> TmpCust : **INSERT**\n(Get CTSCustID, CustID)
CTSCustomer --> TmpUsername : **JOIN**\nON Username

' Flow: Association By Device
SP --> SP : Check ip_HasDevice = 1
SP --> TmpCustDevice : **INSERT**\n(Get Device IDs)
TmpCust --> AssocByDevice : **JOIN**\nON CTSCustID

SP --> TmpCustDevice : **DELETE**\n(Remove devices with no other customers)
note right of SP
    **Filter Logic:**
    - Keep only devices that have
      other customers (not just input customers)
    - Must have CustSubID = 0
end note

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(Device Associations)
TmpCustDevice --> AssocByDevice : **JOIN**\nON DCSDeviceID
AssocByDevice --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON CTSCustID
note right of SP
    **Association By Device:**
    - Find other customers using same device
    - AssociationType = 1
    - Only CustSubID = 0
end note

' Flow: Association By Betting Pattern (AI)
SP --> SP : Check ip_HasAI = 1
SP --> TmpAIAssType : **INSERT**\n(Get Active AI Types)
AssocTypeSetting --> TmpAIAssType : **SELECT**\nWHERE AssTypeID = 2 AND Active

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(AssociationByAI - FromCustID)
TmpCust --> AssocByAI : **JOIN**\nON FromCustID
AssocByAI --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON ToCustID
TmpAIAssType --> AssocByAI : **EXISTS**\nON AssType

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(AssociationByAI - ToCustID)
TmpCust --> AssocByAI : **JOIN**\nON ToCustID
AssocByAI --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON FromCustID
TmpAIAssType --> AssocByAI : **EXISTS**\nON AssType

note right of SP
    **Association By AI (Betting Pattern):**
    - Bidirectional: FromCustID → ToCustID
    - And: ToCustID → FromCustID
    - Filter by active AssType from settings
    - AssociationType = 2
    - Only CustSubID = 0
end note

' Flow: Association By Group (AI)
SP --> TmpCustGroupByAI : **INSERT**\n(Get Group IDs)
TmpCust --> AssocGroupByAI : **JOIN**\nON CustID

SP --> TmpCustGroupByAI : **DELETE**\n(Remove groups with no other customers)
note right of SP
    **Filter Logic:**
    - Keep only groups that have
      other customers (not just input customers)
    - Must have CustSubID = 0
end note

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(GroupByAI Associations)
TmpCustGroupByAI --> AssocGroupByAI : **JOIN**\nON GroupID
AssocGroupByAI --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON CustID
note right of SP
    **Association By Group (AI):**
    - Find other customers in same AI group
    - AssociationType = 2
    - Only CustSubID = 0
end note

' Flow: Association By IP
SP --> SP : Check ip_HasIP = 1
SP --> TmpIPAssType : **INSERT**\n(Get Active IP Types)
AssocTypeSetting --> TmpIPAssType : **SELECT**\nWHERE AssTypeID = 4 AND Active

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(AssociationByIP - FromCustID)
TmpCust --> AssocByIP : **JOIN**\nON FromCustID
AssocByIP --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON ToCustID
TmpIPAssType --> AssocByIP : **EXISTS**\nON AssType

SP --> TmpAssociation : **INSERT**\n(AssociationByIP - ToCustID)
TmpCust --> AssocByIP : **JOIN**\nON ToCustID
AssocByIP --> CTSCustomer : **JOIN**\nON FromCustID
TmpIPAssType --> AssocByIP : **EXISTS**\nON AssType

note right of SP
    **Association By IP:**
    - Bidirectional: FromCustID → ToCustID
    - And: ToCustID → FromCustID
    - Filter by active AssType from settings
    - AssociationType = 4
    - Only CustSubID = 0
end note

' Flow: Return Results
SP --> TmpAssociation : **SELECT**\nGROUP BY RootCustID
note right of SP
    **Returns:**
    - RootCustID
    - AssCustIDList (comma-separated)
      using GROUP_CONCAT
    **Grouping:**
    - GROUP BY RootCustID
    - DISTINCT AssCustID
    - Multiple AssociationTypes per pair
      are allowed (separate rows)
end note

' Cleanup (MySQL auto-drops TEMPORARY tables)
note right of SP
    **Cleanup:**
    MySQL automatically drops
    TEMPORARY tables at end of session
end note

@enduml

